Getting DNS working on your machines is a basic, generic question 
specific to your machines/LAN and not directly related to Heritrix 
operation, so no, this list can&#39;t guide you.

Also, whoever set up your machines and network went through extra effort 
to have some local names, but not all internet names, resolve. So you 
need to take the matter up with them and have them train you on what&#39;s 
possible there.

- Gordon @ IA

