&gt;     I don&#39;t think there&#39;s anything left to troubleshoot. As I mentioned,
&gt;     all current versions of Heritrix assume they will be able to do DNS
&gt;     lookups of all crawled hosts from the crawling machine. (It would
&gt;     require changing the Heritrix code to remove this assumption.)
